			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65031841" name="comment_link_65031841" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23558283&amp;cid=65031841" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65031841)" >Re: "Ghost gun" is a propaganda term...</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65031841" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65031841); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
